      <title>朝鲜宣称成功试射多弹头导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/north-korea-claims-success-in-test-for-multiple-warhead-missile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜声称成功进行了一次多弹头导弹系统的试验，该国试图满足领导人金正恩的目标，即获取可增强其发动核打击能力的技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/north-korea-claims-success-in-test-for-multiple-warhead-missile</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普助手菲利克斯·萨特洗钱案败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ex-trump-associate-felix-sater-loses-ny-money-laundering-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费利克斯·萨特（Felix Sater）是一位出生于莫斯科的交易员，曾是唐纳德·特朗普的核心圈子成员，他在一场民事审判中败诉，他被指控帮助一名富有的哈萨克斯坦男子通过包括特朗普 SoHo 大厦公寓在内的美国房地产洗钱数百万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/ex-trump-associate-felix-sater-loses-ny-money-laundering-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>粉碎政变让玻利维亚总统获得急需的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/bolivia-arrests-former-army-general-who-led-a-coup-attempt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在玻利维亚总统府外，反对社会主义政府的政变失败后，叛军四散而去，高呼口号的人群点燃烟花，挥舞拳头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/bolivia-arrests-former-army-general-who-led-a-coup-attempt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着疫情援助收益到期，芝加哥寻求更多收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/chicago-hunts-for-more-revenue-as-gains-from-pandemic-aid-expire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥领导人周三发起了一场可能很棘手的讨论，重点是如何在未来几年联邦疫情援助逐渐减少的情况下增加收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/chicago-hunts-for-more-revenue-as-gains-from-pandemic-aid-expire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 22:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>圣保罗水务公司股份出售仅吸引一名竞标者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sao-paulo-water-utility-s-privization-said-to-lure-single-bidder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西电力公司赤道能源公司 (Equatorial Energia SA) 已成为竞购 Sabesp 水务公司关键股权的唯一竞标者，圣保罗州正通过数十亿美元的股票发行将 Sabesp 水务公司私有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sao-paulo-water-utility-s-privization-said-to-lure-single-bidder</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 22:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玻利维亚总统阿尔塞在政变后宣誓就任新陆军总司令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/bolivia-presidential-palace-stormed-in-apparent-coup-attempt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚总统路易斯·阿尔塞周三晚间为新任陆军总司令宣誓就职。此前，其前任总统率领的军队于周三袭击总统府，企图发动政变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/bolivia-presidential-palace-stormed-in-apparent-coup-attempt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥的 Sheinbaum 淡化了 AMLO 会从远处指导她的想法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sheinbaum-downplays-idea-that-amlo-would-direct-her-from-afar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆表示，一旦她在墨西哥就职，她的前任和政治导师将不会远程指导她的政府，这回答了人们对安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔是否有可能继续参与政府事务的普遍疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sheinbaum-downplays-idea-that-amlo-would-direct-her-from-afar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:38:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加兰特称美国和以色列缓解了武器“瓶颈”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/us-and-israel-ease-bottlenecks-over-munitions-gallant-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长表示，与白宫高级官员的会谈缓解了向以色列军队供应武器的“瓶颈”，表明双方希望缓解因美国扣留武器的指控而引发的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/us-and-israel-ease-bottlenecks-over-munitions-gallant-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
